      • from

        static OrderBlueprint from(int customer,
                           int width,
                           int length,
                           int height,
                           int roofing,
                           int slope,
                           boolean active,
                           ShedBlueprint shedBlueprint,
                           java.lang.String comment)
        Returns a new order blueprint from the provided information.
        Parameters:
        customer - The customer of the order to specify in the blueprint.
        width - The width of the order to specify in the blueprint.
        length - The length of the order to specify in the blueprint.
        height - The height of the order to specify in the blueprint.
        roofing - The roofing of the order to specify in the blueprint.
        slope - The slope of the order to specify in the blueprint.
        active - Whether or not the order is currently active.
        shedBlueprint - The shed to include in the order. null for no shed.
        comment - The comment left by the customer about the order.
        Returns:
        The newly created order blueprint.
